attributeSource.infoString2: NORTHWOOD REALTY SERVICES UPPER ST CLAIR

data.description: Lovely 3BR 2.5 bath brick ranch. Hardwood floors throughout the first floor. Newer kitchen with granite counter tops, pantry, soft close drawers and SS appliances. Oversized GR with wet bar, neutral carpeting, glass block windows for natural light and a wood burning FP. Overhead fan/light in every bedroom. Large living room with bow window, gas fireplace and stained glass décor on the front door that opens to a beautiful dining room with bow window. Lots of natural light. Updated bathrooms with newer ceramic tile. Custom up-down-bottom-up window shades. Large outdoor rear covered slate patio off kitchen. Large laundry with half bath on lower level. Within minutes and walking distance to Caste Village shops.
